I didn't intend for Sozoku to be wearing a trail duster.<br>
<br>
Anyways, I went and checked to make sure that policemen wore those round hats and western jackets, and sure enough... I was right ^_^ <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.miburo.com/info/9500.jpg">www.miburo.com/info/9500.jpg</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
I found a picture of the actual squad that Saitou Hajime belonged to when he guised himself under the name of Fujita Goro. They're all wearing the forementioned hats and jackets.<br>
<br>
Also, I fixed some narrative errors I had, including some punctuation that was uncalled for (I used a semicolon where a comma was supposed to go at... Stupid me, ne?) It should read better at some parts now.<br>
